eir own leaderboards to dominate! </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Same-screen 2 player Co-Op. For double the fun and available for all game modes and Remote Play Together compatible!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 9 Clans (7 unlockable) to choose from, each with their own weapons, fighting styles, and upgrade paths!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 100+ items. From passives that provide general boosts and benefits, to equipable gear where you can use new tools, weapons and weird artifacts!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 15 different regions (10 unlockable) to adventure through each with their own enemies, hazards, oddities and challenges!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A variety of weird and wonderful sub-stages that alongside the different randomised regions and special rooms helps make each Abyss run feel like a unique experience!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unlockable hats and skin/clothes colour customisations!</li></ul><br><i>~ But perhaps the stories are true? Do the fabled gates really exist? Where may they lead? And who may well dwell in such haunted realms beyond? ~</i><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078200/extras/6b96d9474c7b91a48b692e03ff83f113.poster.avif?t=1731087019\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078200/extras/6b96d9474c7b91a48b692e03ff83f113.webm?t=1731087019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078200/extras/6b96d9474c7b91a48b692e03ff83f113.mp4?t=1731087019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078200/extras/f057ab792be04810008657867af6d066.poster.avif?t=17310